txt.en: For all of your efforts in Adagím and throughout Mûr Ghala the Kintai of Sul Madásh now perceive you as a trustworthy ally.
You continue to prove your value, honesty, and measured assistance to the Kintai Elves of Sul Madásh.
Ally of the Kintai of Sul Madásh
You must earn Ally standing with the Kintai of Sul Madásh
